      "body": "This is supported. [We currently have a \"Coverage\" build type](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/blob/master/CMakeLists.txt#L158), but we figured out that using a build type (like Release, Debug, ...) may be the wrong approach because it results in issues with CMake multi-config generators. \n\nSee https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1592, https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1291, https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1251.",
